# Trivy CVE suppressions.
#
# Every entry below is a vulnerability in a transitive dependency pulled by
# Eclipse EDC 0.15.1 (see `edc` in gradle/libs.versions.toml). They cannot be
# fixed in this repository directly. Each block names the EDC release that
# bumps the affected library past the fix version, or notes that no upstream
# fix is available yet.
#
# Source for the "fixed by EDC ..." mappings: release notes of
# https://github.com/eclipse-edc/Connector (v0.16.0, v0.17.0).
#
# Maintenance: review this file on every EDC bump in libs.versions.toml and
# remove any entry that no longer appears in the scan output.

# Fixed by EDC 0.17.0 (bumps jackson to 2.21.2).
GHSA-72hv-8253-57qq

# Fixed by EDC 0.17.0 (bumps bouncyCastle-jdk18on to 1.84).
# Note: our libs.versions.toml already pins bouncycastle = "1.84" but EDC
# 0.15.1 still drags 1.82 in transitively; the EDC bump removes that path.
CVE-2026-5588
CVE-2026-5598
CVE-2026-0636

# Fixed by EDC 0.17.0 (bumps jetty to 12.1.7).
CVE-2026-2332
CVE-2026-1605

